data.description: 3 bedroom/ 2 bath home situated on just over 6 acres!! If your looking to escape the hustle and bustle of the city then this is the property for you! Nestled away in the country yet just a short drive to the Historic Downtown Arcadia, restaurants, shopping and more. The home sits on a corner lot, which is completely fenced with fresh landscaping around the home. Plenty of room for animals or driving your ATV's! There is even a small pond on the property if you enjoy fishing but don't want to drive to the boat ramp. Property features plenty of room to add a barn, park equipment or a RV or even start your own mini farm. This truly is a beautiful property in a peaceful neighborhood of DeSoto County and with a little TLC this could be your dream home. Call your realtor to schedule your private showings today!
